*label: start

*question: Your message to ChatGPT:
	*type: paragraph
	*save: user_message

>> payload = {}
>> payload["model"] = "gpt-4"
>> payload["messages"] = [ { "role" -> "user", "content" -> user_message } ]

Thinking...

*service: ChatGPT OpenAI API
	*path: /chat/completions
	*method: POST
	*send: payload
	*success
		>> chatgpt_response = it["choices"][1]["message"]["content"]
		>> error = 0
	*error
		>> error = it

*clear

*if: error = 0

	*{"YOU:"}* {user_message}

	*{"CHATGPT:"}* {chatgpt_response}

*if: not (error = 0)

	*{"ERROR:"}* {error}

*goto: start